3606/********************************/
3607/*** RESISTANCE ***/
3608/********************************/
3609
3610void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModResistanceExclusive(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3611{
3612 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3613 return;
3614
3615 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3616
3617 for (int8 x = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; x < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; x++)
3618 {
3619 if (GetMiscValue() & int32(1<<x))
3620 {
3621 int32 amount = target->GetMaxPositiveAuraModifierByMiscMask(SPELL_AURA_MOD_RESISTANCE_EXCLUSIVE, 1<<x, this);
3622 if (amount < GetAmount())
3623 {
3624 float value = float(GetAmount() - amount);
3625 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + x), BASE_VALUE, value, apply);
3626 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
3627 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsMod(SpellSchools(x), aurApp->IsPositive(), value, apply);
3628 }
3629 }
3630 }
3631}
3632
3633void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModResistance(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3634{
3635 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3636 return;
3637
3638 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3639
3640 for (int8 x = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; x < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; x++)
3641 {
3642 if (GetMiscValue() & int32(1<<x))
3643 {
3644 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + x), TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3645 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3646 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsMod(SpellSchools(x), GetAmount() > 0, (float)GetAmount(), apply);
3647 }
3648 }
3649}
3650
3651void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModBaseResistancePCT(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3652{
3653 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3654 return;
3655
3656 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3657
3658 // only players have base stats
3659 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
3660 {
3661 //pets only have base armor
3662 if (target->IsPet() && (GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL))
3663 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_ARMOR, BASE_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3664 }
3665 else
3666 {
3667 for (int8 x = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; x < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; x++)
3668 {
3669 if (GetMiscValue() & int32(1<<x))
3670 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + x), BASE_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3671 }
3672 }
3673}
3674
3675void AuraEffect::HandleModResistancePercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3676{
3677 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3678 return;
3679
3680 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3681 int32 spellGroupVal = target->GetHighestExclusiveSameEffectSpellGroupValue(this, SPELL_AURA_MOD_RESISTANCE_PCT);
3682 if (abs(spellGroupVal) >= abs(GetAmount()))
3683 return;
3684
3685 for (int8 i = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; i++)
3686 {
3687 if (GetMiscValue() & int32(1<<i))
3688 {
3689 if (spellGroupVal)
3690 {
3691 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, (float)spellGroupVal, !apply);
3692 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3693 {
3694 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsPercentMod(SpellSchools(i), true, (float)spellGroupVal, !apply);
3695 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsPercentMod(SpellSchools(i), false, (float)spellGroupVal, !apply);
3696 }
3697 }
3698 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3699 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3700 {
3701 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsPercentMod(SpellSchools(i), true, (float)GetAmount(), apply);
3702 target->ApplyResistanceBuffModsPercentMod(SpellSchools(i), false, (float)GetAmount(), apply);
3703 }
3704 }
3705 }
3706}
3707
3708void AuraEffect::HandleModBaseResistance(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3709{
3710 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3711 return;
3712
3713 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3714
3715 // only players have base stats
3716 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
3717 {
3718 //only pets have base stats
3719 if (target->IsPet() && (GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL))
3720 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_ARMOR, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3721 }
3722 else
3723 {
3724 for (int i = SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; i++)
3725 if (GetMiscValue() & (1<<i))
3726 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_RESISTANCE_START + i), TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3727 }
3728}
3729
3730void AuraEffect::HandleModTargetResistance(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3731{
3732 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3733 return;
3734
3735 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3736
3737 // applied to damage as HandleNoImmediateEffect in Unit::CalcAbsorbResist and Unit::CalcArmorReducedDamage
3738
3739 // show armor penetration
3740 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && (GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL))
3741 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_TARGET_PHYSICAL_RESISTANCE, GetAmount(), apply);
3742
3743 // show as spell penetration only full spell penetration bonuses (all resistances except armor and holy
3744 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && (GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL) == SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL)
3745 target->ApplyModInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_TARGET_RESISTANCE, GetAmount(), apply);
3746}

3748/********************************/
3749/*** STAT ***/
3750/********************************/
3751
3752void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModStat(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3753{
3754 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3755 return;
3756
3757 if (GetMiscValue() < -2 || GetMiscValue() > 4)
3758 {
3759 TC_LOG_ERROR("spells", "WARNING: Spell %u effect %u has an unsupported misc value (%i) for SPELL_AURA_MOD_STAT ", GetId(), GetEffIndex(), GetMiscValue());
3760 return;
3761 }
3762
3763 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3764 int32 spellGroupVal = target->GetHighestExclusiveSameEffectSpellGroupValue(this, SPELL_AURA_MOD_STAT, true, GetMiscValue());
3765 if (abs(spellGroupVal) >= abs(GetAmount()))
3766 return;
3767
3768 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; i++)
3769 {
3770 // -1 or -2 is all stats (misc < -2 checked in function beginning)
3771 if (GetMiscValue() < 0 || GetMiscValue() == i)
3772 {
3773 if (spellGroupVal)
3774 {
3775 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_VALUE, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
3776 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3777 target->ApplyStatBuffMod(Stats(i), float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
3778 }
3779
3780 //target->ApplyStatMod(Stats(i), m_amount, apply);
3781 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3782 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3783 target->ApplyStatBuffMod(Stats(i), (float)GetAmount(), apply);
3784 }
3785 }
3786}
3787
3788void AuraEffect::HandleModPercentStat(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3789{
3790 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3791 return;
3792
3793 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3794
3795 if (GetMiscValue() < -1 || GetMiscValue() > 4)
3796 {
3797 TC_LOG_ERROR("spells", "WARNING: Misc Value for SPELL_AURA_MOD_PERCENT_STAT not valid");
3798 return;
3799 }
3800
3801 // only players have base stats
3802 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
3803 return;
3804
3805 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; ++i)
3806 {
3807 if (GetMiscValue() == i || GetMiscValue() == -1)
3808 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), BASE_PCT, float(m_amount), apply);
3809 }
3810}

3885
3886void AuraEffect::HandleModTotalPercentStat(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
3887{
3888 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
3889 return;
3890
3891 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
3892 int32 spellGroupVal = target->GetHighestExclusiveSameEffectSpellGroupValue(this, SPELL_AURA_MOD_TOTAL_STAT_PERCENTAGE, true, -1);
3893 if (abs(spellGroupVal) >= abs(GetAmount()))
3894 return;
3895
3896 if (spellGroupVal)
3897 {
3898 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; i++)
3899 {
3900 if (GetMiscValue() == i || GetMiscValue() == -1) // affect the same stats
3901 {
3902 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
3903 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3904 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
3905 }
3906 }
3907 }
3908
3909 // save current health state
3910 float healthPct = target->GetHealthPct();
3911 bool alive = target->IsAlive();
3912
3913 for (int32 i = STAT_STRENGTH; i < MAX_STATS; i++)
3914 {
3915 if (GetMiscValueB() & 1 << i || !GetMiscValueB()) // 0 is also used for all stats
3916 {
3917 int32 spellGroupVal2 = target->GetHighestExclusiveSameEffectSpellGroupValue(this, SPELL_AURA_MOD_TOTAL_STAT_PERCENTAGE, true, i);
3918 if (abs(spellGroupVal2) >= abs(GetAmount()))
3919 continue;
3920
3921 if (spellGroupVal2)
3922 {
3923 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, float(spellGroupVal2), !apply);
3924 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3925 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), float(spellGroupVal2), !apply);
3926 }
3927
3928 target->HandleStatModifier(UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_STAT_START + i), TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
3929 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER || target->IsPet())
3930 target->ApplyStatPercentBuffMod(Stats(i), float(GetAmount()), apply);
3931 }
3932 }
3933
3934 // recalculate current HP/MP after applying aura modifications (only for spells with SPELL_ATTR0_UNK4 0x00000010 flag)
3935 // this check is total bullshit i think
3936 if (GetMiscValueB() & 1 << STAT_STAMINA && (m_spellInfo->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR0_ABILITY)))
3937 target->SetHealth(std::max<uint32>(uint32(healthPct * target->GetMaxHealth() * 0.01f), (alive ? 1 : 0)));
3938}

3940void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModResistenceOfStatPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool /*apply*/) const
3941{
3942 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))

3947 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
3948 return;

3950 if (GetMiscValue() != SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL)

3952 // support required adding replace UpdateArmor by loop by UpdateResistence at intellect update
3953 // and include in UpdateResistence same code as in UpdateArmor for aura mod apply.
3954 TC_LOG_ERROR("spells", "Aura SPELL_AURA_MOD_RESISTANCE_OF_STAT_PERCENT(182) does not work for non-armor type resistances!");
3955 return;
3956 }
3957
3958 // Recalculate Armor
3959 target->UpdateArmor();
3960}

4069void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseHealth(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4070{
4071 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4072 return;
4073
4074 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4075
4076 if (apply)
4077 {
4078 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4079 target->ModifyHealth(GetAmount());
4080 }
4081 else
4082 {
4083 if (target->GetHealth() > 0)
4084 {
4085 int32 value = std::min<int32>(target->GetHealth() - 1, GetAmount());
4086 target->ModifyHealth(-value);
4087 }
4088 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4089 }
4090}

4092void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseMaxHealth(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4093{
4094 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4095 return;
4096
4097 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4098
4099 float percent = target->GetHealthPct();
4100
4101 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4102
4103 // refresh percentage
4104 if (target->GetHealth() > 0)
4105 {
4106 uint32 newHealth = std::max<uint32>(target->CountPctFromMaxHealth(int32(percent)), 1);
4107 target->SetHealth(newHealth);
4108 }
4109}
4110
4111void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseEnergy(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4112{
4113 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4114 return;
4115
4116 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4117
4118 Powers powerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
4119 // do not check power type, we can always modify the maximum
4120 // as the client will not see any difference
4121 // also, placing conditions that may change during the aura duration
4122 // inside effect handlers is not a good idea
4123 //if (int32(powerType) != GetMiscValue())
4124 // return;
4125
4126 UnitMods unitMod = UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_POWER_START + powerType);
4127
4128 target->HandleStatModifier(unitMod, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4129}
4130
4131void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseEnergyPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4132{
4133 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4134 return;
4135
4136 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4137
4138 Powers powerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
4139 // do not check power type, we can always modify the maximum
4140 // as the client will not see any difference
4141 // also, placing conditions that may change during the aura duration
4142 // inside effect handlers is not a good idea
4143 //if (int32(powerType) != GetMiscValue())
4144 // return;
4145
4146 UnitMods unitMod = UnitMods(UNIT_MOD_POWER_START + powerType);
4147 float amount = float(GetAmount());
4148
4149 if (apply)
4150 {
4151 target->HandleStatModifier(unitMod, TOTAL_PCT, amount, apply);
4152 target->ModifyPowerPct(powerType, amount, apply);
4153 }
4154 else
4155 {
4156 target->ModifyPowerPct(powerType, amount, apply);
4157 target->HandleStatModifier(unitMod, TOTAL_PCT, amount, apply);
4158 }
4159}
4160
4161void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModIncreaseHealthPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4162{
4163 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4164 return;
4165
4166 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4167
4168 // Unit will keep hp% after MaxHealth being modified if unit is alive.
4169 float percent = target->GetHealthPct();
4170 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_HEALTH, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4171
4172 if (target->GetHealth() > 0)
4173 {
4174 uint32 newHealth = std::max<uint32>(target->CountPctFromMaxHealth(int32(percent)), 1);
4175 target->SetHealth(newHealth);
4176 }
4177}

4245void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModWeaponCritPercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4246{
4247 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4248 return;
4249
4250 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4251
4252 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4253 return;
4254
4255 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_ATTACK; ++i)
4256 if (Item* pItem = target->ToPlayer()->GetWeaponForAttack(WeaponAttackType(i), true))
4257 target->ToPlayer()->_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraCritMod(pItem, WeaponAttackType(i), this, apply);
4258
4259 // mods must be applied base at equipped weapon class and subclass comparison
4260 // with spell->EquippedItemClass and EquippedItemSubClassMask and EquippedItemInventoryTypeMask
4261 // GetMiscValue() comparison with item generated damage types
4262
4263 if (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass == -1)
4264 {
4265 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(CRIT_PERCENTAGE, FLAT_MOD, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4266 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(OFFHAND_CRIT_PERCENTAGE, FLAT_MOD, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4267 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(RANGED_CRIT_PERCENTAGE, FLAT_MOD, float (GetAmount()), apply);
4268 }
4269 else
4270 {
4271 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods
4272 }
4273}

4398 target->ApplyAttackTimePercentMod(RANGED_ATTACK, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
4399 }
4400 target->ApplyCastTimePercentMod(float(m_amount), apply);
4401 target->ApplyAttackTimePercentMod(BASE_ATTACK, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4402 target->ApplyAttackTimePercentMod(OFF_ATTACK, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4403 target->ApplyAttackTimePercentMod(RANGED_ATTACK, float(GetAmount()), apply);

4546/********************************/
4547/*** DAMAGE BONUS ***/
4548/********************************/
4549void AuraEffect::HandleModDamageDone(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4550{
4551 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4552 return;
4553
4554 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4555
4556 // apply item specific bonuses for already equipped weapon
4557 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4558 {
4559 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_ATTACK; ++i)
4560 if (Item* pItem = target->ToPlayer()->GetWeaponForAttack(WeaponAttackType(i), true))
4561 target->ToPlayer()->_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraDamageMod(pItem, WeaponAttackType(i), this, apply);
4562 }
4563
4564 // GetMiscValue() is bitmask of spell schools
4565 // 1 (0-bit) - normal school damage (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL)
4566 // 126 - full bitmask all magic damages (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC) including wands
4567 // 127 - full bitmask any damages
4568 //
4569 // mods must be applied base at equipped weapon class and subclass comparison
4570 // with spell->EquippedItemClass and EquippedItemSubClassMask and EquippedItemInventoryTypeMask
4571 // GetMiscValue() comparison with item generated damage types
4572
4573 if ((GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL) != 0)
4574 {
4575 // apply generic physical damage bonuses including wand case
4576 if (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass == -1 || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4577 {
4578 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_MAINHAND, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4579 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4580 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_RANGED, TOTAL_VALUE, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4581
4582 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4583 {
4584 if (GetAmount() > 0)
4585 target->ApplyModUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_POS, GetAmount(), apply);
4586 else
4587 target->ApplyModUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_NEG, GetAmount(), apply);
4588 }
4589 }
4590 else
4591 {
4592 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods
4593 }
4594 }
4595
4596 // Skip non magic case for speedup
4597 if ((GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC) == 0)
4598 return;
4599
4600 if (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass != -1 || GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemInventoryTypeMask != 0)
4601 {
4602 // wand magic case (skip generic to all item spell bonuses)
4603 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods
4604
4605 // Skip item specific requirements for not wand magic damage
4606 return;
4607 }
4608
4609 // Magic damage modifiers implemented in Unit::SpellDamageBonus
4610 // This information for client side use only
4611 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4612 {
4613 if (GetAmount() > 0)
4614 {
4615 for (int i = SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; i++)
4616 {
4617 if ((GetMiscValue() & (1<<i)) != 0)
4618 target->ApplyModUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_POS+i, GetAmount(), apply);
4619 }
4620 }
4621 else
4622 {
4623 for (int i = SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; i++)
4624 {
4625 if ((GetMiscValue() & (1<<i)) != 0)
4626 target->ApplyModUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_NEG+i, GetAmount(), apply);
4627 }
4628 }
4629 if (Guardian* pet = target->ToPlayer()->GetGuardianPet())
4630 pet->UpdateAttackPowerAndDamage();
4631 }
4632}
4633
4634void AuraEffect::HandleModDamagePercentDone(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4635{
4636 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4637 return;
4638
4639 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4640 int32 spellGroupVal = target->GetHighestExclusiveSameEffectSpellGroupValue(this, SPELL_AURA_MOD_DAMAGE_PERCENT_DONE);
4641 if (abs(spellGroupVal) >= abs(GetAmount()))
4642 return;
4643
4644 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4645 {
4646 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_ATTACK; ++i)
4647 if (Item* item = target->ToPlayer()->GetWeaponForAttack(WeaponAttackType(i), false))
4648 target->ToPlayer()->_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraDamageMod(item, WeaponAttackType(i), this, apply);
4649 }
4650
4651 if ((GetMiscValue() & SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL) && (GetSpellInfo()->EquippedItemClass == -1 || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER))
4652 {
4653 if (spellGroupVal)
4654 {
4655 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_MAINHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
4656 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
4657 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_RANGED, TOTAL_PCT, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
4658 }
4659 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_MAINHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4660 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4661 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_RANGED, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4662
4663 if (Player* player = target->ToPlayer())
4664 {
4665 if (spellGroupVal)
4666 player->ApplyPercentModFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_PCT, float(spellGroupVal), !apply);
4667
4668 player->ApplyPercentModFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_MOD_DAMAGE_DONE_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4669 }
4670 }
4671 else
4672 {
4673 // done in Player::_ApplyWeaponDependentAuraMods for SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL && EquippedItemClass != -1 and also for wand case
4674 }
4675}
4676
4677void AuraEffect::HandleModOffhandDamagePercent(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4678{
4679 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4680 return;
4681
4682 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4683
4684 target->HandleStatModifier(UNIT_MOD_DAMAGE_OFFHAND, TOTAL_PCT, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4685}
4686
4687void AuraEffect::HandleShieldBlockValue(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4688{
4689 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_STAT)))
4690 return;
4691
4692 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4693
4694 BaseModType modType = FLAT_MOD;
4695 if (GetAuraType() == SPELL_AURA_MOD_SHIELD_BLOCKVALUE_PCT)
4696 modType = PCT_MOD;
4697
4698 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4699 target->ToPlayer()->HandleBaseModValue(SHIELD_BLOCK_VALUE, modType, float(GetAmount()), apply);
4700}
4701
4702/********************************/
4703/*** POWER COST ***/
4704/********************************/
4705
4706void AuraEffect::HandleModPowerCostPCT(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4707{
4708 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
4709 return;
4710
4711 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4712
4713 float amount = CalculatePct(1.0f, GetAmount());
4714 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
4715 if (GetMiscValue() & (1 << i))
4716 target->ApplyModSignedFloatValue(UNIT_FIELD_POWER_COST_MULTIPLIER + i, amount, apply);
4717}
4718
4719void AuraEffect::HandleModPowerCost(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4720{
4721 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
4722 return;
4723
4724 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4725
4726 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
4727 if (GetMiscValue() & (1<<i))
4728 target->ApplyModInt32Value(UNIT_FIELD_POWER_COST_MODIFIER+i, GetAmount(), apply);
4729}
4730
4731void AuraEffect::HandleArenaPreparation(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4732{
4733 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4734 return;
4735
4736 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4737
4738 if (apply)
4739 target->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_PREPARATION);
4740 else
4741 {
4742 // do not remove unit flag if there are more than this auraEffect of that kind on unit on unit
4743 if (target->HasAuraType(GetAuraType()))
4744 return;
4745 target->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_PREPARATION);
4746 }
4747}
4748
4749void AuraEffect::HandleNoReagentUseAura(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool /*apply*/) const
4750{
4751 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4752 return;
4753
4754 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4755
4756 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4757 return;
4758
4759 flag128 mask;
4760 Unit::AuraEffectList const& noReagent = target->GetAuraEffectsByType(SPELL_AURA_NO_REAGENT_USE);
4761 for (Unit::AuraEffectList::const_iterator i = noReagent.begin(); i != noReagent.end(); ++i)
4762 if (SpellEffectInfo const* effect = (*i)->GetSpellEffectInfo())
4763 mask |= effect->SpellClassMask;
4764
4765 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1 , mask[0]);
4766 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1+1, mask[1]);
4767 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1+2, mask[2]);
4768 target->SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_NO_REAGENT_COST_1+3, mask[3]);
4769}
4770
4771void AuraEffect::HandleAuraRetainComboPoints(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4772{
4773 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4774 return;
4775
4776 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4777
4778 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
4779 return;
4780
4781 // combo points was added in SPELL_EFFECT_ADD_COMBO_POINTS handler
4782 // remove only if aura expire by time (in case combo points amount change aura removed without combo points lost)
4783 if (!apply && aurApp->GetRemoveMode() == AURA_REMOVE_BY_EXPIRE)
4784 target->ToPlayer()->AddComboPoints(-GetAmount());
4785}

4788/*** OTHERS ***/
4789/*********************************************************/
4790
4791void AuraEffect::HandleAuraDummy(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
4792{
4793 if (!(mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAPPLY)))
4794 return;
4795
4796 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
4797
4798 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
4799
4800 if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL)
4801 {
4802 // pet auras
4803 if (PetAura const* petSpell = sSpellMgr->GetPetAura(GetId(), m_effIndex))
4804 {
4805 if (apply)
4806 target->AddPetAura(petSpell);
4807 else
4808 target->RemovePetAura(petSpell);
4809 }
4810 }
4811
4812 if (mode & (AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL | AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAPPLY))
4813 {
4814 // AT APPLY
4815 if (apply)
4816 {
4817 switch (GetId())
4818 {
4819 case 1515: // Tame beast
4820 // FIX_ME: this is 2.0.12 threat effect replaced in 2.1.x by dummy aura, must be checked for correctness
4821 if (caster && target->CanHaveThreatList())
4822 target->AddThreat(caster, 10.0f);
4823 break;
4824 case 13139: // net-o-matic
4825 // root to self part of (root_target->charge->root_self sequence
4826 if (caster)
4827 caster->CastSpell(caster, 13138, true, NULL, this);
4828 break;
4829 case 34026: // kill command
4830 {
4831 Unit* pet = target->GetGuardianPet();
4832 if (!pet)
4833 break;
4834
4835 target->CastSpell(target, 34027, true, NULL, this);
4836
4837 // set 3 stacks and 3 charges (to make all auras not disappear at once)
4838 Aura* owner_aura = target->GetAura(34027, GetCasterGUID());
4839 Aura* pet_aura = pet->GetAura(58914, GetCasterGUID());
4840 if (owner_aura)
4841 {
4842 owner_aura->SetStackAmount(owner_aura->GetSpellInfo()->StackAmount);
4843 if (pet_aura)
4844 {
4845 pet_aura->SetCharges(0);
4846 pet_aura->SetStackAmount(owner_aura->GetSpellInfo()->StackAmount);
4847 }
4848 }
4849 break;
4850 }
4851 case 37096: // Blood Elf Illusion
4852 {
4853 if (caster)
4854 {
4855 if (caster->getGender() == GENDER_FEMALE)
4856 caster->CastSpell(target, 37095, true, NULL, this); // Blood Elf Disguise
4857 else
4858 caster->CastSpell(target, 37093, true, NULL, this);
4859 }
4860 break;
4861 }
4862 case 39850: // Rocket Blast
4863 if (roll_chance_i(20)) // backfire stun
4864 target->CastSpell(target, 51581, true, NULL, this);
4865 break;
4866 case 43873: // Headless Horseman Laugh
4867 target->PlayDistanceSound(11965);
4868 break;
4869 case 46354: // Blood Elf Illusion
4870 if (caster)
4871 {
4872 if (caster->getGender() == GENDER_FEMALE)
4873 caster->CastSpell(target, 46356, true, NULL, this);
4874 else
4875 caster->CastSpell(target, 46355, true, NULL, this);
4876 }
4877 break;
4878 case 46361: // Reinforced Net
4879 if (caster)
4880 target->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFall();
4881 break;
4882 case 71563:
4883 if (Aura* newAura = target->AddAura(71564, target))
4884 newAura->SetStackAmount(newAura->GetSpellInfo()->StackAmount);
4885 break;
4886 }
4887 }
4888 // AT REMOVE
4889 else
4890 {
4891 if ((GetSpellInfo()->IsQuestTame()) && caster && caster->IsAlive() && target->IsAlive())
4892 {
4893 uint32 finalSpelId = 0;
4894 switch (GetId())
4895 {
4896 case 19548: finalSpelId = 19597; break;
4897 case 19674: finalSpelId = 19677; break;
4898 case 19687: finalSpelId = 19676; break;
4899 case 19688: finalSpelId = 19678; break;
4900 case 19689: finalSpelId = 19679; break;
4901 case 19692: finalSpelId = 19680; break;
4902 case 19693: finalSpelId = 19684; break;
4903 case 19694: finalSpelId = 19681; break;
4904 case 19696: finalSpelId = 19682; break;
4905 case 19697: finalSpelId = 19683; break;
4906 case 19699: finalSpelId = 19685; break;
4907 case 19700: finalSpelId = 19686; break;
4908 case 30646: finalSpelId = 30647; break;
4909 case 30653: finalSpelId = 30648; break;
4910 case 30654: finalSpelId = 30652; break;
4911 case 30099: finalSpelId = 30100; break;
4912 case 30102: finalSpelId = 30103; break;
4913 case 30105: finalSpelId = 30104; break;
4914 }
4915
4916 if (finalSpelId)
4917 caster->CastSpell(target, finalSpelId, true, NULL, this);
4918 }
4919
4920 switch (m_spellInfo->SpellFamilyName)
4921 {
4922 case SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC:
4923 switch (GetId())
4924 {
4925 case 2584: // Waiting to Resurrect
4926 // Waiting to resurrect spell cancel, we must remove player from resurrect queue
4927 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
4928 {
4929 if (Battleground* bg = target->ToPlayer()->GetBattleground())
4930 bg->RemovePlayerFromResurrectQueue(target->GetGUID());
4931 if (Battlefield* bf = sBattlefieldMgr->GetBattlefieldToZoneId(target->GetZoneId()))
4932 bf->RemovePlayerFromResurrectQueue(target->GetGUID());
4933 }
4934 break;
4935 case 36730: // Flame Strike
4936 {
4937 target->CastSpell(target, 36731, true, NULL, this);
4938 break;
4939 }
4940 case 44191: // Flame Strike
4941 {
4942 if (target->GetMap()->IsDungeon())
4943 {
4944 uint32 spellId = target->GetMap()->IsHeroic() ? 46163 : 44190;
4945
4946 target->CastSpell(target, spellId, true, NULL, this);
4947 }
4948 break;
4949 }
4950 case 43681: // Inactive
4951 {
4952 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || aurApp->GetRemoveMode() != AURA_REMOVE_BY_EXPIRE)
4953 return;
4954
4955 if (target->GetMap()->IsBattleground())
4956 target->ToPlayer()->LeaveBattleground();
4957 break;
4958 }
4959 case 42783: // Wrath of the Astromancer
4960 target->CastSpell(target, GetAmount(), true, NULL, this);
4961 break;
4962 case 46308: // Burning Winds cast only at creatures at spawn
4963 target->CastSpell(target, 47287, true, NULL, this);
4964 break;
4965 case 52172: // Coyote Spirit Despawn Aura
4966 case 60244: // Blood Parrot Despawn Aura
4967 target->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, GetAmount(), true, NULL, this);
4968 break;
4969 case 91604: // Restricted Flight Area
4970 if (aurApp->GetRemoveMode() == AURA_REMOVE_BY_EXPIRE)
4971 target->CastSpell(target, 58601, true);
4972 break;
4973 }
4974 break;
4975 case SPELLFAMILY_DEATHKNIGHT:
4976 // Summon Gargoyle (Dismiss Gargoyle at remove)
4977 if (GetId() == 61777)
4978 target->CastSpell(target, GetAmount(), true);
4979 break;
4980 default:
4981 break;
4982 }
4983 }
4984 }
4985
4986 // AT APPLY & REMOVE
4987
4988 switch (m_spellInfo->SpellFamilyName)
4989 {
4990 case SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC:
4991 {
4992 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
4993 break;
4994 switch (GetId())
4995 {
4996 // Recently Bandaged
4997 case 11196:
4998 target->ApplySpellImmune(GetId(), IMMUNITY_MECHANIC, GetMiscValue(), apply);
4999 break;
5000 // Unstable Power
5001 case 24658:
5002 {
5003 uint32 spellId = 24659;
5004 if (apply && caster)
5005 {
5006 SpellInfo const* spell = sSpellMgr->AssertSpellInfo(spellId);
5007
5008 for (uint32 i = 0; i < spell->StackAmount; ++i)
5009 caster->CastSpell(target, spell->Id, true, NULL, NULL, GetCasterGUID());
5010 break;
5011 }
5012 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(spellId);
5013 break;
5014 }
5015 // Restless Strength
5016 case 24661:
5017 {
5018 uint32 spellId = 24662;
5019 if (apply && caster)
5020 {
5021 SpellInfo const* spell = sSpellMgr->AssertSpellInfo(spellId);
5022 for (uint32 i = 0; i < spell->StackAmount; ++i)
5023 caster->CastSpell(target, spell->Id, true, NULL, NULL, GetCasterGUID());
5024 break;
5025 }
5026 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(spellId);
5027 break;
5028 }
5029 // Tag Murloc
5030 case 30877:
5031 {
5032 // Tag/untag Blacksilt Scout
5033 target->SetEntry(apply ? 17654 : 17326);
5034 break;
5035 }
5036 case 57819: // Argent Champion
5037 case 57820: // Ebon Champion
5038 case 57821: // Champion of the Kirin Tor
5039 case 57822: // Wyrmrest Champion
5040 {
5041 if (!caster || caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5042 break;
5043
5044 uint32 FactionID = 0;
5045
5046 if (apply)
5047 {
5048 switch (m_spellInfo->Id)
5049 {
5050 case 57819: FactionID = 1106; break; // Argent Crusade
5051 case 57820: FactionID = 1098; break; // Knights of the Ebon Blade
5052 case 57821: FactionID = 1090; break; // Kirin Tor
5053 case 57822: FactionID = 1091; break; // The Wyrmrest Accord
5054 }
5055 }
5056 caster->ToPlayer()->SetChampioningFaction(FactionID);
5057 break;
5058 }
5059 // LK Intro VO (1)
5060 case 58204:
5061 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5062 {
5063 // Play part 1
5064 if (apply)
5065 target->PlayDirectSound(14970, target->ToPlayer());
5066 // continue in 58205
5067 else
5068 target->CastSpell(target, 58205, true);
5069 }
5070 break;
5071 // LK Intro VO (2)
5072 case 58205:
5073 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5074 {
5075 // Play part 2
5076 if (apply)
5077 target->PlayDirectSound(14971, target->ToPlayer());
5078 // Play part 3
5079 else
5080 target->PlayDirectSound(14972, target->ToPlayer());
5081 }
5082 break;
5083 }
5084
5085 break;
5086 }
5087 case SPELLFAMILY_MAGE:
5088 {
5089 //if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5090 //break;
5091 break;
5092 }
5093 case SPELLFAMILY_PRIEST:
5094 {
5095 //if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5096 //break;
5097 break;
5098 }
5099 case SPELLFAMILY_DRUID:
5100 {
5101 //if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5102 //break;
5103 break;
5104 }
5105 case SPELLFAMILY_SHAMAN:
5106 {
5107 //if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5108 //break;
5109 break;
5110 }
5111 case SPELLFAMILY_PALADIN:
5112 // if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5113 // break;
5114 break;
5115 case SPELLFAMILY_DEATHKNIGHT:
5116 {
5117 //if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5118 // break;
5119 break;
5120 }
5121 }

5123
5124void AuraEffect::HandleChannelDeathItem(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5125{
5126 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5127 return;
5128
5129 if (apply || aurApp->GetRemoveMode() != AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEATH)
5130 return;
5131
5132 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
5133
5134 if (!caster || caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5135 return;
5136
5137 Player* plCaster = caster->ToPlayer();
5138 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5139
5140 // Item amount
5141 if (GetAmount() <= 0)
5142 return;
5143
5144 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->ItemType == 0)
5145 return;
5146
5147 // Soul Shard
5148 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->ItemType == 6265)
5149 {
5150 // Soul Shard only from units that grant XP or honor
5151 if (!plCaster->isHonorOrXPTarget(target) ||
5152 (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT && !target->ToCreature()->isTappedBy(plCaster)))
5153 return;
5154 }
5155
5156 //Adding items
5157 uint32 noSpaceForCount = 0;
5158 uint32 count = m_amount;
5159
5160 ItemPosCountVec dest;
5161 InventoryResult msg = plCaster->CanStoreNewItem(NULL_BAG, NULL_SLOT, dest, GetSpellEffectInfo()->ItemType, count, &noSpaceForCount);
5162 if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5163 {
5164 count-=noSpaceForCount;
5165 plCaster->SendEquipError(msg, NULL, NULL, GetSpellEffectInfo()->ItemType);
5166 if (count == 0)
5167 return;
5168 }
5169
5170 Item* newitem = plCaster->StoreNewItem(dest, GetSpellEffectInfo()->ItemType, true);
5171 if (!newitem)
5172 {
5173 plCaster->SendEquipError(EQUIP_ERR_ITEM_NOT_FOUND, NULL, NULL);
5174 return;
5175 }
5176 plCaster->SendNewItem(newitem, count, true, true);
5177}
5178
5179void AuraEffect::HandleBindSight(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5180{
5181 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5182 return;
5183
5184 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5185
5186 Unit* caster = GetCaster();
5187
5188 if (!caster || caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5189 return;
5190
5191 caster->ToPlayer()->SetViewpoint(target, apply);
5192}
5193
5194void AuraEffect::HandleForceReaction(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5195{
5196 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
5197 return;
5198
5199 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5200
5201 Player* player = target->ToPlayer();
5202 if (!player)
5203 return;
5204
5205 uint32 factionId = GetMiscValue();
5206 ReputationRank factionRank = ReputationRank(m_amount);
5207
5208 player->GetReputationMgr().ApplyForceReaction(factionId, factionRank, apply);
5209 player->GetReputationMgr().SendForceReactions();
5210
5211 // stop fighting if at apply forced rank friendly or at remove real rank friendly
5212 if ((apply && factionRank >= REP_FRIENDLY) || (!apply && player->GetReputationRank(factionId) >= REP_FRIENDLY))
5213 player->StopAttackFaction(factionId);
5214}
5215
5216void AuraEffect::HandleAuraEmpathy(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5217{
5218 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5219 return;
5220
5221 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5222 if (!apply)
5223 {
5224 // do not remove unit flag if there are more than this auraEffect of that kind on unit on unit
5225 if (target->HasAuraType(GetAuraType()))
5226 return;
5227 }
5228
5229 if (target->GetCreatureType() == CREATURE_TYPE_BEAST)
5230 target->ApplyModUInt32Value(OBJECT_DYNAMIC_FLAGS, UNIT_DYNFLAG_SPECIALINFO, apply);
5231}
5232
5233void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModFaction(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5234{
5235 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5236 return;
5237
5238 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5239
5240 if (apply)
5241 {
5242 target->setFaction(GetMiscValue());
5243 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5244 target->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_PVP_ATTACKABLE);
5245 }
5246 else
5247 {
5248 target->RestoreFaction();
5249 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5250 target->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_PVP_ATTACKABLE);
5251 }
5252}

5257 return;

5260

5262 target->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS_2, UNIT_FLAG2_COMPREHEND_LANG);
5263 else
5264 {
5265 if (target->HasAuraType(GetAuraType()))
5266 return;
