5268 target->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS_2, UNIT_FLAG2_COMPREHEND_LANG);
5269 }
5270}
5271
5272void AuraEffect::HandleAuraConvertRune(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5273{
5274 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5275 return;
5276
5277 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5278
5279 Player* player = target->ToPlayer();
5280 if (!player)
5281 return;
5282
5283 if (player->getClass() != CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
5284 return;
5285
5286 uint32 runes = m_amount;
5287 // convert number of runes specified in aura amount of rune type in miscvalue to runetype in miscvalueb
5288 if (apply)
5289 {
5290 for (uint32 i = 0; i < MAX_RUNES && runes; ++i)
5291 {
5292 if (GetMiscValue() != player->GetCurrentRune(i))
5293 continue;
5294 if (!player->GetRuneCooldown(i))
5295 {
5296 player->AddRuneByAuraEffect(i, RuneType(GetMiscValueB()), this);
5297 --runes;
5298 }
5299 }
5300 }
5301 else
5302 player->RemoveRunesByAuraEffect(this);
5303}
5304
5305void AuraEffect::HandleAuraLinked(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5306{
5307 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5308
5309 uint32 triggeredSpellId = GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell;
5310 SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggeredSpellId);
5311 if (!triggeredSpellInfo)
5312 return;
5313
5314 Unit* caster = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, target->GetMap()->GetDifficultyID()) ? GetCaster() : target;
5315 if (!caster)
5316 return;
5317
5318 if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL)
5319 {
5320 if (apply)
5321 {
5322 // If amount avalible cast with basepoints (Crypt Fever for example)
5323 if (GetAmount())
5324 caster->CastCustomSpell(target, triggeredSpellId, &m_amount, NULL, NULL, true, NULL, this);
5325 else
5326 caster->CastSpell(target, triggeredSpellId, true, NULL, this);
5327 }
5328 else
5329 {
5330 ObjectGuid casterGUID = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, caster->GetMap()->GetDifficultyID()) ? GetCasterGUID() : target->GetGUID();
5331 target->RemoveAura(triggeredSpellId, casterGUID, 0, aurApp->GetRemoveMode());
5332 }
5333 }
5334 else if (mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAPPLY && apply)
5335 {
5336 ObjectGuid casterGUID = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, caster->GetMap()->GetDifficultyID()) ? GetCasterGUID() : target->GetGUID();
5337 // change the stack amount to be equal to stack amount of our aura
5338 if (Aura* triggeredAura = target->GetAura(triggeredSpellId, casterGUID))
5339 triggeredAura->ModStackAmount(GetBase()->GetStackAmount() - triggeredAura->GetStackAmount());
5340 }
5341}
5342
5343void AuraEffect::HandleAuraOpenStable(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5344{
5345 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5346 return;
5347
5348 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5349
5350 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || !target->IsInWorld())
5351 return;
5352
5353 if (apply)
5354 target->ToPlayer()->GetSession()->SendStablePet(target->GetGUID());
5355
5356 // client auto close stable dialog at !apply aura
5357}
5358
5359void AuraEffect::HandleAuraModFakeInebriation(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5360{
5361 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_CHANGE_AMOUNT_MASK))
5362 return;
5363
5364 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5365
5366 if (apply)
5367 {
5368 target->m_invisibilityDetect.AddFlag(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK);
5369 target->m_invisibilityDetect.AddValue(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK, GetAmount());
5370
5371 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5372 {
5373 int32 oldval = target->ToPlayer()->GetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION);
5374 target->ToPlayer()->SetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION, oldval + GetAmount());
5375 }
5376 }
5377 else
5378 {
5379 bool removeDetect = !target->HasAuraType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_FAKE_INEBRIATE);
5380
5381 target->m_invisibilityDetect.AddValue(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK, -GetAmount());
5382
5383 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
5384 {
5385 int32 oldval = target->ToPlayer()->GetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION);
5386 target->ToPlayer()->SetInt32Value(PLAYER_FAKE_INEBRIATION, oldval - GetAmount());
5387
5388 if (removeDetect)
5389 removeDetect = !target->ToPlayer()->GetDrunkValue();
5390 }
5391
5392 if (removeDetect)
5393 target->m_invisibilityDetect.DelFlag(INVISIBILITY_DRUNK);
5394 }
5395
5396 // call functions which may have additional effects after chainging state of unit
5397 target->UpdateObjectVisibility();
5398}
5399
5400void AuraEffect::HandleAuraOverrideSpells(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5401{
5402 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5403 return;
5404
5405 Player* target = aurApp->GetTarget()->ToPlayer();
5406
5407 if (!target || !target->IsInWorld())
5408 return;
5409
5410 uint32 overrideId = uint32(GetMiscValue());
5411
5412 if (apply)
5413 {
5414 target->SetUInt16Value(PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES2, PLAYER_BYTES_2_OVERRIDE_SPELLS_UINT16_OFFSET, overrideId);
5415 if (OverrideSpellDataEntry const* overrideSpells = sOverrideSpellDataStore.LookupEntry(overrideId))
5416 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_OVERRIDE_SPELL; ++i)
5417 if (uint32 spellId = overrideSpells->SpellID[i])
5418 target->AddTemporarySpell(spellId);
5419 }
5420 else
5421 {
5422 target->SetUInt16Value(PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES2, PLAYER_BYTES_2_OVERRIDE_SPELLS_UINT16_OFFSET, 0);
5423 if (OverrideSpellDataEntry const* overrideSpells = sOverrideSpellDataStore.LookupEntry(overrideId))
5424 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_OVERRIDE_SPELL; ++i)
5425 if (uint32 spellId = overrideSpells->SpellID[i])
5426 target->RemoveTemporarySpell(spellId);
5427 }
5428}
5429
5430void AuraEffect::HandleAuraSetVehicle(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5431{
5432 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5433 return;
5434
5435 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
5436
5437 if (!target->IsInWorld())
5438 return;
5439
5440 uint32 vehicleId = GetMiscValue();
5441
5442 if (apply)
5443 {
5444 if (!target->CreateVehicleKit(vehicleId, 0))
5445 return;
5446 }
5447 else if (target->GetVehicleKit())
5448 target->RemoveVehicleKit();
5449
5450 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5451 return;
5452
5453 if (apply)
5454 target->ToPlayer()->SendOnCancelExpectedVehicleRideAura();
5455}
5456
5457void AuraEffect::HandlePreventResurrection(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
5458{
5459 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5460 return;
5461
5462 if (aurApp->GetTarget()->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5463 return;
5464
5465 if (apply)
5466 aurApp->GetTarget()->RemoveFlag(PLAYER_FIELD_LOCAL_FLAGS, PLAYER_LOCAL_FLAG_RELEASE_TIMER);
5467 else if (!aurApp->GetTarget()->GetBaseMap()->Instanceable())
5468 aurApp->GetTarget()->SetFlag(PLAYER_FIELD_LOCAL_FLAGS, PLAYER_LOCAL_FLAG_RELEASE_TIMER);
5469}
5470
5471void AuraEffect::HandleMastery(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool /*apply*/) const
5472{
5473 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
5474 return;
5475
5476 Player* target = aurApp->GetTarget()->ToPlayer();
5477 if (!target)
5478 return;
5479
5480 target->UpdateMastery();
5481}
5482
5483void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicDummyAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
5484{
5485 switch (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyName)
5486 {
5487 case SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC:
5488 switch (GetId())
5489 {
5490 case 66149: // Bullet Controller Periodic - 10 Man
5491 case 68396: // Bullet Controller Periodic - 25 Man
5492 {
5493 if (!caster)
5494 break;
5495
5496 caster->CastCustomSpell(66152, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, urand(1, 6), target, true);
5497 caster->CastCustomSpell(66153, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, urand(1, 6), target, true);
5498 break;
5499 }
5500 case 62292: // Blaze (Pool of Tar)
5501 // should we use custom damage?
5502 target->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell, true);
5503 break;
5504 case 62399: // Overload Circuit
5505 if (target->GetMap()->IsDungeon() && int(target->GetAppliedAuras().count(62399)) >= (target->GetMap()->IsHeroic() ? 4 : 2))
5506 {
5507 target->CastSpell(target, 62475, true); // System Shutdown
5508 if (Unit* veh = target->GetVehicleBase())
5509 veh->CastSpell(target, 62475, true);
5510 }
5511 break;
5512 case 64821: // Fuse Armor (Razorscale)
5513 if (GetBase()->GetStackAmount() == GetSpellInfo()->StackAmount)
5514 {
5515 target->CastSpell(target, 64774, true, NULL, NULL, GetCasterGUID());
5516 target->RemoveAura(64821);
5517 }
5518 break;
5519 }
5520 break;
5521 case SPELLFAMILY_MAGE:
5522 {
5523 // Mirror Image
5524 if (GetId() == 55342)
5525 // Set name of summons to name of caster
5526 target->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell, true);
5527 break;
5528 }
5529 case SPELLFAMILY_DRUID:
5530 {
5531 switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
5532 {
5533 // Frenzied Regeneration
5534 case 22842:
5535 {
5536 // Converts up to 10 rage per second into health for $d. Each point of rage is converted into ${$m2/10}.1% of max health.
5537 // Should be manauser
5538 if (target->getPowerType() != POWER_RAGE)
5539 break;
5540 uint32 rage = target->GetPower(POWER_RAGE);
5541 // Nothing todo
5542 if (rage == 0)
5543 break;
5544 int32 mod = (rage < 100) ? rage : 100;
5545 int32 points = target->CalculateSpellDamage(target, GetSpellInfo(), 1);
5546 int32 regen = target->GetMaxHealth() * (mod * points / 10) / 1000;
5547 target->CastCustomSpell(target, 22845, &regen, nullptr, nullptr, true, nullptr, this);
5548 target->SetPower(POWER_RAGE, rage-mod);
5549 break;
5550 }
5551 }
5552 break;
5553 }
5554 case SPELLFAMILY_HUNTER:
5555 {
5556 // Explosive Shot
5557 if (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyFlags[1] & 0x80000000)
5558 {
5559 if (caster)
5560 caster->CastCustomSpell(53352, SPELLVALUE_BASE_POINT0, m_amount, target, true, NULL, this);
5561 break;
5562 }
5563 switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
5564 {
5565 // Feeding Frenzy Rank 1
5566 case 53511:
5567 if (target->GetVictim() && target->EnsureVictim()->HealthBelowPct(35))
5568 target->CastSpell(target, 60096, true, nullptr, this);
5569 return;
5570 // Feeding Frenzy Rank 2
5571 case 53512:
5572 if (target->GetVictim() && target->EnsureVictim()->HealthBelowPct(35))
5573 target->CastSpell(target, 60097, true, nullptr, this);
5574 return;
5575 default:
5576 break;
5577 }
5578 break;
5579 }
5580 case SPELLFAMILY_SHAMAN:
5581 if (GetId() == 52179) // Astral Shift
5582 {
5583 // Periodic need for remove visual on stun/fear/silence lost
5584 if (!(target->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS)&(UNIT_FLAG_STUNNED|UNIT_FLAG_FLEEING|UNIT_FLAG_SILENCED)))
5585 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(52179);
5586 break;
5587 }
5588 break;
5589 case SPELLFAMILY_DEATHKNIGHT:
5590 switch (GetId())
5591 {
5592 case 49016: // Hysteria
5593 uint32 damage = uint32(target->CountPctFromMaxHealth(1));
5594 target->DealDamage(target, damage, NULL, NODAMAGE, SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL, NULL, false);
5595 break;
5596 }
5597 // Blood of the North
5598 // Reaping
5599 // Death Rune Mastery
5600 if (GetSpellInfo()->SpellIconID == 3041 || GetSpellInfo()->SpellIconID == 22 || GetSpellInfo()->SpellIconID == 2622)
5601 {
5602 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
5603 return;
5604 if (target->ToPlayer()->getClass() != CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
5605 return;
5606
5607 // timer expired - remove death runes
5608 target->ToPlayer()->RemoveRunesByAuraEffect(this);
5609 }
5610 break;
5611 default:
5612 break;
5613 }
5614}
5615
5616void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicTriggerSpellAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
5617{
5618 // generic casting code with custom spells and target/caster customs
5619 uint32 triggerSpellId = GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell;
5620
5621 SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggerSpellId);
5622 SpellInfo const* auraSpellInfo = GetSpellInfo();
5623 uint32 auraId = auraSpellInfo->Id;
5624
5625 // specific code for cases with no trigger spell provided in field
5626 if (triggeredSpellInfo == NULL)
5627 {
5628 switch (auraSpellInfo->SpellFamilyName)
5629 {
5630 case SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC:
5631 {
5632 switch (auraId)
5633 {
5634 // Brood Affliction: Bronze
5635 case 23170:
5636 triggerSpellId = 23171;
5637 break;
5638 // Restoration
5639 case 24379:
5640 case 23493:
5641 {
5642 if (caster)
5643 {
5644 int32 heal = caster->CountPctFromMaxHealth(10);
5645 caster->HealBySpell(target, auraSpellInfo, heal);
5646
5647 if (int32 mana = caster->GetMaxPower(POWER_MANA))
5648 {
5649 mana /= 10;
5650 caster->EnergizeBySpell(caster, 23493, mana, POWER_MANA);
5651 }
5652 }
5653 return;
5654 }
5655 // Nitrous Boost
5656 case 27746:
5657 if (caster && target->GetPower(POWER_MANA) >= 10)
5658 {
5659 target->ModifyPower(POWER_MANA, -10);
5660 target->SendEnergizeSpellLog(caster, 27746, 10, POWER_MANA);
5661 }
5662 else
5663 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(27746);
5664 return;
5665 // Frost Blast
5666 case 27808:
5667 if (caster)
5668 caster->CastCustomSpell(29879, SPELLVALUE_BASE_POINT0, int32(target->CountPctFromMaxHealth(21)), target, true, NULL, this);
5669 return;
5670 // Inoculate Nestlewood Owlkin
5671 case 29528:
5672 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_UNIT) // prevent error reports in case ignored player target
5673 return;
5674 break;
5675 // Feed Captured Animal
5676 case 29917:
5677 triggerSpellId = 29916;
5678 break;
5679 // Extract Gas
5680 case 30427:
5681 {
5682 // move loot to player inventory and despawn target
5683 if (caster && caster->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER &&
5684 target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_UNIT &&
5685 target->ToCreature()->GetCreatureTemplate()->type == CREATURE_TYPE_GAS_CLOUD)
5686 {
5687 Player* player = caster->ToPlayer();
5688 Creature* creature = target->ToCreature();
5689 // missing lootid has been reported on startup - just return
5690 if (!creature->GetCreatureTemplate()->SkinLootId)
5691 return;
5692
5693 player->AutoStoreLoot(creature->GetCreatureTemplate()->SkinLootId, LootTemplates_Skinning, true);
5694
5695 creature->DespawnOrUnsummon();
5696 }
5697 return;
5698 }
5699 // Quake
5700 case 30576:
5701 triggerSpellId = 30571;
5702 break;
5703 // Doom
5704 /// @todo effect trigger spell may be independant on spell targets, and executed in spell finish phase
5705 // so instakill will be naturally done before trigger spell
5706 case 31347:
5707 {
5708 target->CastSpell(target, 31350, true, NULL, this);
5709 target->KillSelf();
5710 return;
5711 }
5712 // Spellcloth
5713 case 31373:
5714 {
5715 // Summon Elemental after create item
5716 target->SummonCreature(17870, 0, 0, 0, target->GetOrientation(), TEMPSUMMON_DEAD_DESPAWN, 0);
5717 return;
5718 }
5719 // Flame Quills
5720 case 34229:
5721 {
5722 // cast 24 spells 34269-34289, 34314-34316
5723 for (uint32 spell_id = 34269; spell_id != 34290; ++spell_id)
5724 target->CastSpell(target, spell_id, true, NULL, this);
5725 for (uint32 spell_id = 34314; spell_id != 34317; ++spell_id)
5726 target->CastSpell(target, spell_id, true, NULL, this);
5727 return;
5728 }
5729 // Remote Toy
5730 case 37027:
5731 triggerSpellId = 37029;
5732 break;
5733 // Eye of Grillok
5734 case 38495:
5735 triggerSpellId = 38530;
5736 break;
5737 // Absorb Eye of Grillok (Zezzak's Shard)
5738 case 38554:
5739 {
5740 if (!caster || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_UNIT)
5741 return;
5742
5743 caster->CastSpell(caster, 38495, true, NULL, this);
5744
5745 Creature* creatureTarget = target->ToCreature();
5746
5747 creatureTarget->DespawnOrUnsummon();
5748 return;
5749 }
5750 // Tear of Azzinoth Summon Channel - it's not really supposed to do anything, and this only prevents the console spam
5751 case 39857:
5752 triggerSpellId = 39856;
5753 break;
5754 // Personalized Weather
5755 case 46736:
5756 triggerSpellId = 46737;
5757 break;
5758 }
5759 break;
5760 }
5761 case SPELLFAMILY_SHAMAN:
5762 {
5763 switch (auraId)
5764 {
5765 // Lightning Shield (The Earthshatterer set trigger after cast Lighting Shield)
5766 case 28820:
5767 {
5768 // Need remove self if Lightning Shield not active
5769 if (!target->GetAuraEffect(SPELL_AURA_PROC_TRIGGER_SPELL, SPELLFAMILY_SHAMAN, flag128(0x400, 0, 0)))
5770 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(28820);
5771 return;
5772 }
5773 // Totemic Mastery (Skyshatter Regalia (Shaman Tier 6) - bonus)
5774 case 38443:
5775 {
5776 bool all = true;
5777 for (int i = SUMMON_SLOT_TOTEM; i < MAX_TOTEM_SLOT; ++i)
5778 {
5779 if (!target->m_SummonSlot[i])
5780 {
5781 all = false;
5782 break;
5783 }
5784 }
5785
5786 if (all)
5787 target->CastSpell(target, 38437, true, NULL, this);
5788 else
5789 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(38437);
5790 return;
5791 }
5792 }
5793 break;
5794 }
5795 default:
5796 break;
5797 }
5798 }
5799 else
5800 {
5801 // Spell exist but require custom code
5802 switch (auraId)
5803 {
5804 // Pursuing Spikes (Anub'arak)
5805 case 65920:
5806 case 65922:
5807 case 65923:
5808 {
5809 Unit* permafrostCaster = NULL;
5810 Aura* permafrostAura = target->GetAura(66193);
5811 if (!permafrostAura)
5812 permafrostAura = target->GetAura(67855);
5813 if (!permafrostAura)
5814 permafrostAura = target->GetAura(67856);
5815 if (!permafrostAura)
5816 permafrostAura = target->GetAura(67857);
5817
5818 if (permafrostAura)
5819 permafrostCaster = permafrostAura->GetCaster();
5820
5821 if (permafrostCaster)
5822 {
5823 if (Creature* permafrostCasterCreature = permafrostCaster->ToCreature())
5824 permafrostCasterCreature->DespawnOrUnsummon(3000);
5825
5826 target->CastSpell(target, 66181, false);
5827 target->RemoveAllAuras();
5828 if (Creature* targetCreature = target->ToCreature())
5829 targetCreature->DisappearAndDie();
5830 }
5831 break;
5832 }
5833 // Mana Tide
5834 case 16191:
5835 target->CastCustomSpell(target, triggerSpellId, &m_amount, NULL, NULL, true, NULL, this);
5836 return;
5837 // Negative Energy Periodic
5838 case 46284:
5839 target->CastCustomSpell(triggerSpellId, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, m_tickNumber / 10 + 1, NULL, true, NULL, this);
5840 return;
5841 // Slime Pool (Dreadscale & Acidmaw)
5842 case 66882:
5843 target->CastCustomSpell(triggerSpellId, SPELLVALUE_RADIUS_MOD, (int32)((((float)m_tickNumber / 60) * 0.9f + 0.1f) * 10000 * 2 / 3), NULL, true, NULL, this);
5844 return;
5845 // Slime Spray - temporary here until preventing default effect works again
5846 // added on 9.10.2010
5847 case 69508:
5848 {
5849 if (caster)
5850 caster->CastSpell(target, triggerSpellId, true, NULL, NULL, caster->GetGUID());
5851 return;
5852 }
5853 case 24745: // Summon Templar, Trigger
5854 case 24747: // Summon Templar Fire, Trigger
5855 case 24757: // Summon Templar Air, Trigger
5856 case 24759: // Summon Templar Earth, Trigger
5857 case 24761: // Summon Templar Water, Trigger
5858 case 24762: // Summon Duke, Trigger
5859 case 24766: // Summon Duke Fire, Trigger
5860 case 24769: // Summon Duke Air, Trigger
5861 case 24771: // Summon Duke Earth, Trigger
5862 case 24773: // Summon Duke Water, Trigger
5863 case 24785: // Summon Royal, Trigger
5864 case 24787: // Summon Royal Fire, Trigger
5865 case 24791: // Summon Royal Air, Trigger
5866 case 24792: // Summon Royal Earth, Trigger
5867 case 24793: // Summon Royal Water, Trigger
5868 {
5869 // All this spells trigger a spell that requires reagents; if the
5870 // triggered spell is cast as "triggered", reagents are not consumed
5871 if (caster)
5872 caster->CastSpell(target, triggerSpellId, false);
5873 return;
5874 }
5875 }
5876 }
5877
5878 // Reget trigger spell proto
5879 triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggerSpellId);
5880
5881 if (triggeredSpellInfo)
5882 {
5883 if (Unit* triggerCaster = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, target->GetMap()->GetDifficultyID()) ? caster : target)
5884 {
5885 triggerCaster->CastSpell(target, triggeredSpellInfo, true, NULL, this);
5886 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicTriggerSpellAuraTick: Spell %u Trigger %u", GetId(), triggeredSpellInfo->Id);
5887 }
5888 }
5889 else
5890 {
5891 Creature* c = target->ToCreature();
5892 if (!c || !caster || !sScriptMgr->OnDummyEffect(caster, GetId(), SpellEffIndex(GetEffIndex()), target->ToCreature()) ||
5893 !c->AI()->sOnDummyEffect(caster, GetId(), SpellEffIndex(GetEffIndex())))
5894 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicTriggerSpellAuraTick: Spell %u has non-existent spell %u in EffectTriggered[%d] and is therefor not triggered.", GetId(), triggerSpellId, GetEffIndex());
5895 }
5896}
5897
5898void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicTriggerSpellWithValueAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
5899{
5900 uint32 triggerSpellId = GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell;
5901 if (SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggerSpellId))
5902 {
5903 if (Unit* triggerCaster = triggeredSpellInfo->NeedsToBeTriggeredByCaster(m_spellInfo, target->GetMap()->GetDifficultyID()) ? caster : target)
5904 {
5905 int32 basepoints = GetAmount();
5906 triggerCaster->CastCustomSpell(target, triggerSpellId, &basepoints, &basepoints, &basepoints, true, nullptr, this);
5907 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicTriggerSpellWithValueAuraTick: Spell %u Trigger %u", GetId(), triggeredSpellInfo->Id);
5908 }
5909 }
5910 else
5911 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells","AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicTriggerSpellWithValueAuraTick: Spell %u has non-existent spell %u in EffectTriggered[%d] and is therefor not triggered.", GetId(), triggerSpellId, GetEffIndex());
5912}
5913
5914void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicDamageAurasTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
5915{
5916 if (!caster || !target->IsAlive())
5917 return;
5918
5919 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED) || target->IsImmunedToDamage(GetSpellInfo()))
5920 {
5921 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
5922 return;
5923 }
5924
5925 // Consecrate ticks can miss and will not show up in the combat log
5926 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_PERSISTENT_AREA_AURA &&
5927 caster->SpellHitResult(target, GetSpellInfo(), false) != SPELL_MISS_NONE)
5928 return;
5929
5930 // some auras remove at specific health level or more
5931 if (GetAuraType() == SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE)
5932 {
5933 switch (GetSpellInfo()->Id)
5934 {
5935 case 43093: case 31956: case 38801: // Grievous Wound
5936 case 35321: case 38363: case 39215: // Gushing Wound
5937 if (target->IsFullHealth())
5938 {
5939 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(GetSpellInfo()->Id);
5940 return;
5941 }
5942 break;
5943 case 38772: // Grievous Wound
5944 {
5945 if (SpellEffectInfo const* effect = GetSpellInfo()->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, EFFECT_1))
5946 {
5947 uint32 percent = effect->CalcValue(caster);
5948 if (!target->HealthBelowPct(percent))
5949 {
5950 target->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(GetSpellInfo()->Id);
5951 return;
5952 }
5953 }
5954 break;
5955 }
5956 }
5957 }
5958
5959 uint32 absorb = 0;
5960 uint32 resist = 0;
5961 CleanDamage cleanDamage = CleanDamage(0, 0, BASE_ATTACK, MELEE_HIT_NORMAL);
5962
5963 // AOE spells are not affected by the new periodic system.
5964 bool isAreaAura = GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsAreaAuraEffect() || GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsEffect(SPELL_EFFECT_PERSISTENT_AREA_AURA);
5965 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
5966 uint32 damage = isAreaAura ? std::max(GetAmount(), 0) : m_damage;
5967
5968 // Script Hook For HandlePeriodicDamageAurasTick -- Allow scripts to change the Damage pre class mitigation calculations
5969 if (isAreaAura)
5970 sScriptMgr->ModifyPeriodicDamageAurasTick(target, caster, damage);
5971
5972 if (GetAuraType() == SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE)
5973 {
5974 if (isAreaAura)
5975 damage = caster->SpellDamageBonusDone(target, GetSpellInfo(), damage, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount()) * caster->SpellDamagePctDone(target, m_spellInfo, DOT);
5976 damage = target->SpellDamageBonusTaken(caster, GetSpellInfo(), damage, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount());
5977
5978 // Calculate armor mitigation
5979 if (caster->IsDamageReducedByArmor(GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), GetSpellInfo(), GetEffIndex()))
5980 {
5981 uint32 damageReductedArmor = caster->CalcArmorReducedDamage(target, damage, GetSpellInfo());
5982 cleanDamage.mitigated_damage += damage - damageReductedArmor;
5983 damage = damageReductedArmor;
5984 }
5985
5986 // Curse of Agony damage-per-tick calculation
5987 if (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_WARLOCK && (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyFlags[0] & 0x400) && GetSpellInfo()->SpellIconID == 544)
5988 {
5989 uint32 totalTick = GetTotalTicks();
5990 // 1..4 ticks, 1/2 from normal tick damage
5991 if (m_tickNumber <= totalTick / 3)
5992 damage = damage/2;
5993 // 9..12 ticks, 3/2 from normal tick damage
5994 else if (m_tickNumber > totalTick * 2 / 3)
5995 damage += (damage+1)/2; // +1 prevent 0.5 damage possible lost at 1..4 ticks
5996 // 5..8 ticks have normal tick damage
5997 }
5998 // There is a Chance to make a Soul Shard when Drain soul does damage
5999 if (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_WARLOCK && (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyFlags[0] & 0x00004000))
6000 {
6001 if (caster->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && caster->ToPlayer()->isHonorOrXPTarget(target))
6002 caster->CastSpell(caster, 95810, true, 0, this);
6003 }
6004 if (GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_GENERIC)
6005 {
6006 switch (GetId())
6007 {
6008 case 70911: // Unbound Plague
6009 case 72854: // Unbound Plague
6010 case 72855: // Unbound Plague
6011 case 72856: // Unbound Plague
6012 damage *= uint32(pow(1.25f, int32(m_tickNumber)));
6013 break;
6014 default:
6015 break;
6016 }
6017 }
6018 }
6019 else
6020 damage = uint32(target->CountPctFromMaxHealth(damage));
6021
6022 if (!m_spellInfo->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR4_FIXED_DAMAGE))
6023 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsTargetingArea() || isAreaAura)
6024 {
6025 damage = int32(float(damage) * target->GetTotalAuraMultiplierByMiscMask(SPELL_AURA_MOD_AOE_DAMAGE_AVOIDANCE, m_spellInfo->SchoolMask));
6026 if (caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
6027 damage = int32(float(damage) * target->GetTotalAuraMultiplierByMiscMask(SPELL_AURA_MOD_CREATURE_AOE_DAMAGE_AVOIDANCE, m_spellInfo->SchoolMask));
6028 }
6029
6030 bool crit = false;
6031
6032 if (CanPeriodicTickCrit(caster))
6033 crit = roll_chance_f(isAreaAura ? caster->GetUnitSpellCriticalChance(target, m_spellInfo, m_spellInfo->GetSchoolMask()) : m_critChance);
6034
6035 if (crit)
6036 damage = caster->SpellCriticalDamageBonus(m_spellInfo, damage, target);
6037
6038 int32 dmg = damage;
6039
6040 if (!(GetSpellInfo()->AttributesEx4 & SPELL_ATTR4_FIXED_DAMAGE))
6041 caster->ApplyResilience(target, &dmg);
6042 damage = dmg;
6043
6044 caster->CalcAbsorbResist(target, GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), DOT, damage, &absorb, &resist, GetSpellInfo());
6045
6046 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells.periodic", "PeriodicTick: %s attacked %s for %u dmg inflicted by %u absorb is %u",
6047 GetCasterGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), damage, GetId(), absorb);
6048
6049 caster->DealDamageMods(target, damage, &absorb);
6050
6051 // Set trigger flag
6052 uint32 procAttacker = PROC_FLAG_DONE_PERIODIC;
6053 uint32 procVictim = PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_PERIODIC;
6054 uint32 procEx = (crit ? PROC_EX_CRITICAL_HIT : PROC_EX_NORMAL_HIT) | PROC_EX_INTERNAL_DOT;
6055 damage = (damage <= absorb+resist) ? 0 : (damage-absorb-resist);
6056 if (damage)
6057 procVictim |= PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_DAMAGE;
6058
6059 int32 overkill = damage - target->GetHealth();
6060 if (overkill < 0)
6061 overkill = 0;
6062
6063 SpellPeriodicAuraLogInfo pInfo(this, damage, overkill, absorb, resist, 0.0f, crit);
6064
6065 caster->ProcDamageAndSpell(target, procAttacker, procVictim, procEx, damage, BASE_ATTACK, GetSpellInfo());
6066 caster->DealDamage(target, damage, &cleanDamage, DOT, GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), GetSpellInfo(), true);
6067 target->SendPeriodicAuraLog(&pInfo);
6068}
6069
6070bool AuraEffect::IsAreaAuraEffect() const
6071{
6072 if (_effectInfo->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AREA_AURA_PARTY ||
6073 _effectInfo->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AREA_AURA_RAID ||
6074 _effectInfo->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AREA_AURA_FRIEND ||
6075 _effectInfo->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AREA_AURA_ENEMY ||
6076 _effectInfo->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AREA_AURA_PET ||
6077 _effectInfo->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AREA_AURA_OWNER)
6078 return true;
6079 return false;
6080}
6081
6082void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicHealthLeechAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6083{
6084 if (!caster || !target->IsAlive())
6085 return;
6086
6087 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED) || target->IsImmunedToDamage(GetSpellInfo()))
6088 {
6089 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6090 return;
6091 }
6092
6093 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_PERSISTENT_AREA_AURA &&
6094 caster->SpellHitResult(target, GetSpellInfo(), false) != SPELL_MISS_NONE)
6095 return;
6096
6097 uint32 absorb = 0;
6098 uint32 resist = 0;
6099 CleanDamage cleanDamage = CleanDamage(0, 0, BASE_ATTACK, MELEE_HIT_NORMAL);
6100
6101 bool isAreaAura = GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsAreaAuraEffect() || GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsEffect(SPELL_EFFECT_PERSISTENT_AREA_AURA);
6102 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
6103 uint32 damage = isAreaAura ? std::max(GetAmount(), 0) : m_damage;
6104
6105 if (isAreaAura)
6106 {
6107 // Script Hook For HandlePeriodicDamageAurasTick -- Allow scripts to change the Damage pre class mitigation calculations
6108 sScriptMgr->ModifyPeriodicDamageAurasTick(target, caster, damage);
6109 damage = caster->SpellDamageBonusDone(target, GetSpellInfo(), damage, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount()) * caster->SpellDamagePctDone(target, m_spellInfo, DOT);
6110 }
6111 damage = target->SpellDamageBonusTaken(caster, GetSpellInfo(), damage, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount());
6112
6113 // Calculate armor mitigation
6114 if (caster->IsDamageReducedByArmor(GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), GetSpellInfo(), GetEffIndex()))
6115 {
6116 uint32 damageReductedArmor = caster->CalcArmorReducedDamage(target, damage, GetSpellInfo());
6117 cleanDamage.mitigated_damage += damage - damageReductedArmor;
6118 damage = damageReductedArmor;
6119 }
6120
6121 if (!m_spellInfo->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR4_FIXED_DAMAGE))
6122 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsTargetingArea() || isAreaAura)
6123 {
6124 damage = int32(float(damage) * target->GetTotalAuraMultiplierByMiscMask(SPELL_AURA_MOD_AOE_DAMAGE_AVOIDANCE, m_spellInfo->SchoolMask));
6125 if (caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
6126 damage = int32(float(damage) * target->GetTotalAuraMultiplierByMiscMask(SPELL_AURA_MOD_CREATURE_AOE_DAMAGE_AVOIDANCE, m_spellInfo->SchoolMask));
6127 }
6128
6129 bool crit = false;
6130
6131 if (CanPeriodicTickCrit(caster))
6132 crit = roll_chance_f(isAreaAura ? caster->GetUnitSpellCriticalChance(target, m_spellInfo, m_spellInfo->GetSchoolMask()) : m_critChance);
6133
6134 if (crit)
6135 damage = caster->SpellCriticalDamageBonus(m_spellInfo, damage, target);
6136
6137 int32 dmg = damage;
6138 if (!(GetSpellInfo()->AttributesEx4 & SPELL_ATTR4_FIXED_DAMAGE))
6139 caster->ApplyResilience(target, &dmg);
6140 damage = dmg;
6141
6142 caster->CalcAbsorbResist(target, GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), DOT, damage, &absorb, &resist, m_spellInfo);
6143
6144 if (target->GetHealth() < damage)
6145 damage = uint32(target->GetHealth());
6146
6147 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells.periodic", "PeriodicTick: %s health leech of %s for %u dmg inflicted by %u abs is %u",
6148 GetCasterGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), damage, GetId(), absorb);
6149
6150 SpellNonMeleeDamage log(caster, target, GetId(), GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask());
6151 log.damage = damage - absorb - resist;
6152 log.absorb = absorb;
6153 log.resist = resist;
6154 log.periodicLog = true;
6155 if (crit)
6156 log.HitInfo |= SPELL_HIT_TYPE_CRIT;
6157
6158 // Set trigger flag
6159 uint32 procAttacker = PROC_FLAG_DONE_PERIODIC;
6160 uint32 procVictim = PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_PERIODIC;
6161 uint32 procEx = (crit ? PROC_EX_CRITICAL_HIT : PROC_EX_NORMAL_HIT) | PROC_EX_INTERNAL_DOT;
6162 damage = (damage <= absorb+resist) ? 0 : (damage-absorb-resist);
6163 if (damage)
6164 procVictim |= PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_DAMAGE;
6165 if (caster->IsAlive())
6166 caster->ProcDamageAndSpell(target, procAttacker, procVictim, procEx, damage, BASE_ATTACK, GetSpellInfo());
6167 int32 new_damage = caster->DealDamage(target, damage, &cleanDamage, DOT, GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), GetSpellInfo(), false);
6168 if (caster->IsAlive())
6169 {
6170 float gainMultiplier = GetSpellEffectInfo()->CalcValueMultiplier(caster);
6171
6172 uint32 heal = uint32(caster->SpellHealingBonusDone(caster, GetSpellInfo(), uint32(new_damage * gainMultiplier), DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount()));
6173 heal = uint32(caster->SpellHealingBonusTaken(caster, GetSpellInfo(), heal, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount()));
6174
6175 int32 gain = caster->HealBySpell(caster, GetSpellInfo(), heal);
6176 caster->getHostileRefManager().threatAssist(caster, gain * 0.5f, GetSpellInfo());
6177 }
6178
6179 caster->SendSpellNonMeleeDamageLog(&log);
6180}
6181
6182void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicHealthFunnelAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6183{
6184 if (!caster || !caster->IsAlive() || !target->IsAlive())
6185 return;
6186
6187 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED))
6188 {
6189 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6190 return;
6191 }
6192
6193 uint32 damage = std::max(GetAmount(), 0);
6194 // do not kill health donator
6195 if (caster->GetHealth() < damage)
6196 damage = caster->GetHealth() - 1;
6197 if (!damage)
6198 return;
6199
6200 caster->ModifyHealth(-(int32)damage);
6201 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "PeriodicTick: donator %u target %u damage %u.", caster->GetEntry(), target->GetEntry(), damage);
6202
6203 float gainMultiplier = GetSpellEffectInfo()->CalcValueMultiplier(caster);
6204
6205 damage = int32(damage * gainMultiplier);
6206
6207 caster->HealBySpell(target, GetSpellInfo(), damage);
6208}
6209
6210void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicHealAurasTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6211{
6212 if (!caster || !target->IsAlive())
6213 return;
6214
6215 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED))
6216 {
6217 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6218 return;
6219 }
6220
6221 // heal for caster damage (must be alive)
6222 if (target != caster && GetSpellInfo()->AttributesEx2 & SPELL_ATTR2_HEALTH_FUNNEL && !caster->IsAlive())
6223 return;
6224
6225 // don't regen when permanent aura target has full power
6226 if (GetBase()->IsPermanent() && target->IsFullHealth())
6227 return;
6228
6229 bool isAreaAura = GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsAreaAuraEffect() || GetSpellEffectInfo()->IsEffect(SPELL_EFFECT_PERSISTENT_AREA_AURA);
6230 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
6231 int32 damage = isAreaAura ? std::max(GetAmount(), 0) : m_damage;
6232
6233 if (GetAuraType() == SPELL_AURA_OBS_MOD_HEALTH)
6234 {
6235 // Taken mods
6236 float TakenTotalMod = 1.0f;
6237
6238 // Tenacity increase healing % taken
6239 if (AuraEffect const* Tenacity = target->GetAuraEffect(58549, 0))
6240 AddPct(TakenTotalMod, Tenacity->GetAmount());
6241
6242 // Healing taken percent
6243 float minval = (float)target->GetMaxNegativeAuraModifier(SPELL_AURA_MOD_HEALING_PCT);
6244 if (minval)
6245 AddPct(TakenTotalMod, minval);
6246
6247 float maxval = (float)target->GetMaxPositiveAuraModifier(SPELL_AURA_MOD_HEALING_PCT);
6248 if (maxval)
6249 AddPct(TakenTotalMod, maxval);
6250
6251 TakenTotalMod = std::max(TakenTotalMod, 0.0f);
6252
6253 damage = uint32(target->CountPctFromMaxHealth(damage));
6254 damage = uint32(damage * TakenTotalMod);
6255 }
6256 else
6257 {
6258 // Wild Growth = amount + (6 - 2*doneTicks) * ticks* amount / 100
6259 if (m_spellInfo->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_DRUID && m_spellInfo->SpellIconID == 2864)
6260 {
6261 int32 addition = int32(float(damage * GetTotalTicks()) * ((6-float(2*(GetTickNumber()-1)))/100));
6262
6263 // Item - Druid T10 Restoration 2P Bonus
6264 if (AuraEffect* aurEff = caster->GetAuraEffect(70658, 0))
6265 // divided by 50 instead of 100 because calculated as for every 2 tick
6266 addition += abs(int32((addition * aurEff->GetAmount()) / 50));
6267
6268 damage += addition;
6269 }
6270 if (isAreaAura)
6271 damage = caster->SpellHealingBonusDone(target, GetSpellInfo(), damage, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount()) * caster->SpellHealingPctDone(target, m_spellInfo);
6272 damage = target->SpellHealingBonusTaken(caster, GetSpellInfo(), damage, DOT, GetSpellEffectInfo(), GetBase()->GetStackAmount());
6273 }
6274
6275 bool crit = false;
6276
6277 if (CanPeriodicTickCrit(caster))
6278 crit = roll_chance_f(isAreaAura ? caster->GetUnitSpellCriticalChance(target, m_spellInfo, m_spellInfo->GetSchoolMask()) : m_critChance);
6279
6280 if (crit)
6281 damage = caster->SpellCriticalHealingBonus(m_spellInfo, damage, target);
6282
6283 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells.periodic", "PeriodicTick: %s heal of %s for %u health inflicted by %u",
6284 GetCasterGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), damage, GetId());
6285
6286 uint32 absorb = 0;
6287 uint32 heal = uint32(damage);
6288 caster->CalcHealAbsorb(target, GetSpellInfo(), heal, absorb);
6289 int32 gain = caster->DealHeal(target, heal);
6290
6291 SpellPeriodicAuraLogInfo pInfo(this, heal, heal - gain, absorb, 0, 0.0f, crit);
6292 target->SendPeriodicAuraLog(&pInfo);
6293
6294 target->getHostileRefManager().threatAssist(caster, float(gain) * 0.5f, GetSpellInfo());
6295
6296 uint32 procAttacker = PROC_FLAG_DONE_PERIODIC;
6297 uint32 procVictim = PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_PERIODIC;
6298 uint32 procEx = (crit ? PROC_EX_CRITICAL_HIT : PROC_EX_NORMAL_HIT) | PROC_EX_INTERNAL_HOT;
6299 // ignore item heals
6300 if (GetBase()->GetCastItemGUID().IsEmpty())
6301 caster->ProcDamageAndSpell(target, procAttacker, procVictim, procEx, damage, BASE_ATTACK, GetSpellInfo());
6302}
6303
6304void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicManaLeechAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6305{
6306 Powers powerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
6307
6308 if (!caster || !caster->IsAlive() || !target->IsAlive() || target->getPowerType() != powerType)
6309 return;
6310
6311 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED) || target->IsImmunedToDamage(GetSpellInfo()))
6312 {
6313 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6314 return;
6315 }
6316
6317 if (GetSpellEffectInfo()->Effect == SPELL_EFFECT_PERSISTENT_AREA_AURA &&
6318 caster->SpellHitResult(target, GetSpellInfo(), false) != SPELL_MISS_NONE)
6319 return;
6320
6321 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
6322 int32 drainAmount = std::max(m_amount, 0);
6323
6324 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells.periodic", "PeriodicTick: %s power leech of %s for %u dmg inflicted by %u",
6325 GetCasterGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), drainAmount, GetId());
6326
6327 int32 drainedAmount = -target->ModifyPower(powerType, -drainAmount);
6328
6329 float gainMultiplier = GetSpellEffectInfo()->CalcValueMultiplier(caster);
6330
6331 SpellPeriodicAuraLogInfo pInfo(this, drainedAmount, 0, 0, 0, gainMultiplier, false);
6332
6333 int32 gainAmount = int32(drainedAmount * gainMultiplier);
6334 int32 gainedAmount = 0;
6335 if (gainAmount)
6336 {
6337 gainedAmount = caster->ModifyPower(powerType, gainAmount);
6338 target->AddThreat(caster, float(gainedAmount) * 0.5f, GetSpellInfo()->GetSchoolMask(), GetSpellInfo());
6339 }
6340
6341 // Drain Mana
6342 if (m_spellInfo->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_WARLOCK
6343 && m_spellInfo->SpellFamilyFlags[0] & 0x00000010)
6344 {
6345 int32 manaFeedVal = 0;
6346 if (AuraEffect const* aurEff = GetBase()->GetEffect(1))
6347 manaFeedVal = aurEff->GetAmount();
6348 // Mana Feed - Drain Mana
6349 if (manaFeedVal > 0)
6350 {
6351 int32 feedAmount = CalculatePct(gainedAmount, manaFeedVal);
6352 caster->CastCustomSpell(caster, 32554, &feedAmount, NULL, NULL, true, NULL, this);
6353 }
6354 }
6355
6356 target->SendPeriodicAuraLog(&pInfo);
6357}
6358
6359void AuraEffect::HandleObsModPowerAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6360{
6361 Powers powerType;
6362 if (GetMiscValue() == POWER_ALL)
6363 powerType = target->getPowerType();
6364 else
6365 powerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
6366
6367 if (!target->IsAlive() || !target->GetMaxPower(powerType))
6368 return;
6369
6370 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED))
6371 {
6372 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6373 return;
6374 }
6375
6376 // don't regen when permanent aura target has full power
6377 if (GetBase()->IsPermanent() && target->GetPower(powerType) == target->GetMaxPower(powerType))
6378 return;
6379
6380 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
6381 uint32 amount = std::max(m_amount, 0) * target->GetMaxPower(powerType) /100;
6382 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells.periodic", "PeriodicTick: %s energize %s for %u dmg inflicted by %u",
6383 GetCasterGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), amount, GetId());
6384
6385 SpellPeriodicAuraLogInfo pInfo(this, amount, 0, 0, 0, 0.0f, false);
6386 int32 gain = target->ModifyPower(powerType, amount);
6387
6388 if (caster)
6389 target->getHostileRefManager().threatAssist(caster, float(gain) * 0.5f, GetSpellInfo());
6390
6391 target->SendPeriodicAuraLog(&pInfo);
6392}
6393
6394void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicEnergizeAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6395{
6396 Powers powerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
6397
6398 if (target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && target->getPowerType() != powerType && !m_spellInfo->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR7_CAN_RESTORE_SECONDARY_POWER))
6399 return;
6400
6401 if (!target->IsAlive() || !target->GetMaxPower(powerType))
6402 return;
6403
6404 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED))
6405 {
6406 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6407 return;
6408 }
6409
6410 // don't regen when permanent aura target has full power
6411 if (GetBase()->IsPermanent() && target->GetPower(powerType) == target->GetMaxPower(powerType))
6412 return;
6413
6414 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
6415 int32 amount = std::max(m_amount, 0);
6416
6417 SpellPeriodicAuraLogInfo pInfo(this, amount, 0, 0, 0, 0.0f, false);
6418
6419 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells.periodic", "PeriodicTick: %s energize %s for %u dmg inflicted by %u",
6420 GetCasterGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), amount, GetId());
6421
6422 int32 gain = target->ModifyPower(powerType, amount);
6423 target->SendPeriodicAuraLog(&pInfo);
6424
6425 if (caster)
6426 target->getHostileRefManager().threatAssist(caster, float(gain) * 0.5f, GetSpellInfo());
6427}
6428
6429void AuraEffect::HandlePeriodicPowerBurnAuraTick(Unit* target, Unit* caster) const
6430{
6431 Powers powerType = Powers(GetMiscValue());
6432
6433 if (!caster || !target->IsAlive() || target->getPowerType() != powerType)
6434 return;
6435
6436 if (target->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ISOLATED) || target->IsImmunedToDamage(GetSpellInfo()))
6437 {
6438 SendTickImmune(target, caster);
6439 return;
6440 }
6441
6442 // ignore negative values (can be result apply spellmods to aura damage
6443 int32 damage = std::max(m_amount, 0);
6444
6445 uint32 gain = uint32(-target->ModifyPower(powerType, -damage));
6446
6447 float dmgMultiplier = GetSpellEffectInfo()->CalcValueMultiplier(caster);
6448
6449 SpellInfo const* spellProto = GetSpellInfo();
6450 // maybe has to be sent different to client, but not by SMSG_PERIODICAURALOG
6451 SpellNonMeleeDamage damageInfo(caster, target, spellProto->Id, spellProto->SchoolMask);
6452 // no SpellDamageBonus for burn mana
6453 caster->CalculateSpellDamageTaken(&damageInfo, int32(gain * dmgMultiplier), spellProto);
6454
6455 caster->DealDamageMods(damageInfo.target, damageInfo.damage, &damageInfo.absorb);
6456
6457 // Set trigger flag
6458 uint32 procAttacker = PROC_FLAG_DONE_PERIODIC;
6459 uint32 procVictim = PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_PERIODIC;
6460 uint32 procEx = createProcExtendMask(&damageInfo, SPELL_MISS_NONE) | PROC_EX_INTERNAL_DOT;
6461 if (damageInfo.damage)
6462 procVictim |= PROC_FLAG_TAKEN_DAMAGE;
6463
6464 caster->ProcDamageAndSpell(damageInfo.target, procAttacker, procVictim, procEx, damageInfo.damage, BASE_ATTACK, spellProto);
6465
6466 caster->DealSpellDamage(&damageInfo, true);
6467 caster->SendSpellNonMeleeDamageLog(&damageInfo);
6468}
6469
6470void AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellAuraProc(AuraApplication* aurApp, ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
6471{
6472 Unit* triggerCaster = aurApp->GetTarget();
6473 Unit* triggerTarget = eventInfo.GetProcTarget();
6474
6475 uint32 triggerSpellId = GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell;
6476 if (SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggerSpellId))
6477 {
6478 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellAuraProc: Triggering spell %u from aura %u proc", triggeredSpellInfo->Id, GetId());
6479 triggerCaster->CastSpell(triggerTarget, triggeredSpellInfo, true, NULL, this);
6480 }
6481 else
6482 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells","AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellAuraProc: Could not trigger spell %u from aura %u proc, because the spell does not have an entry in Spell.dbc.", triggerSpellId, GetId());
6483}

6485void AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellWithValueAuraProc(AuraApplication* aurApp, ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
6486{
6487 Unit* triggerCaster = aurApp->GetTarget();
6488 Unit* triggerTarget = eventInfo.GetProcTarget();
6489
6490 uint32 triggerSpellId = GetSpellEffectInfo()->TriggerSpell;
6491 if (SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggerSpellId))
6492 {
6493 int32 basepoints0 = GetAmount();
6494 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellWithValueAuraProc: Triggering spell %u with value %d from aura %u proc", triggeredSpellInfo->Id, basepoints0, GetId());
6495 triggerCaster->CastCustomSpell(triggerTarget, triggerSpellId, &basepoints0, NULL, NULL, true, NULL, this);
6496 }
6497 else
6498 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells","AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellWithValueAuraProc: Could not trigger spell %u from aura %u proc, because the spell does not have an entry in Spell.dbc.", triggerSpellId, GetId());
6499}

6501void AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerDamageAuraProc(AuraApplication* aurApp, ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
6502{
6503 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
6504 Unit* triggerTarget = eventInfo.GetProcTarget();
6505 SpellNonMeleeDamage damageInfo(target, triggerTarget, GetId(), GetSpellInfo()->SchoolMask);
6506 uint32 damage = target->SpellDamageBonusDone(triggerTarget, GetSpellInfo(), GetAmount(), SPELL_DIRECT_DAMAGE, GetSpellEffectInfo());
6507 damage = triggerTarget->SpellDamageBonusTaken(target, GetSpellInfo(), damage, SPELL_DIRECT_DAMAGE, GetSpellEffectInfo());
6508 target->CalculateSpellDamageTaken(&damageInfo, damage, GetSpellInfo());
6509 target->DealDamageMods(damageInfo.target, damageInfo.damage, &damageInfo.absorb);
6510 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerDamageAuraProc: Triggering %u spell damage from aura %u proc", damage, GetId());
6511 target->DealSpellDamage(&damageInfo, true);
6512 target->SendSpellNonMeleeDamageLog(&damageInfo);
6513}
6514
6515void AuraEffect::HandleRaidProcFromChargeAuraProc(AuraApplication* aurApp, ProcEventInfo& /*eventInfo*/)
6516{
6517 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
6518
6519 uint32 triggerSpellId;
6520 switch (GetId())
6521 {
6522 case 57949: // Shiver
6523 triggerSpellId = 57952;
6524 //animationSpellId = 57951; dummy effects for jump spell have unknown use (see also 41637)
6525 break;
6526 case 59978: // Shiver
6527 triggerSpellId = 59979;
6528 break;
6529 case 43593: // Cold Stare
6530 triggerSpellId = 43594;
6531 break;
6532 default:
6533 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleRaidProcFromChargeAuraProc: received not handled spell: %u", GetId());
6534 return;
6535 }
6536
6537 int32 jumps = GetBase()->GetCharges();
6538
6539 // current aura expire on proc finish
6540 GetBase()->SetCharges(0);
6541 GetBase()->SetUsingCharges(true);
6542
6543 // next target selection
6544 if (jumps > 0)
6545 {
6546 if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
6547 {
6548 float radius = GetSpellEffectInfo()->CalcRadius(caster);
6549
6550 if (Unit* triggerTarget = target->GetNextRandomRaidMemberOrPet(radius))
6551 {
6552 target->CastSpell(triggerTarget, GetSpellInfo(), true, NULL, this, GetCasterGUID());
6553 if (Aura* aura = triggerTarget->GetAura(GetId(), GetCasterGUID()))
6554 aura->SetCharges(jumps);
6555 }
6556 }
6557 }
6558
6559 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleRaidProcFromChargeAuraProc: Triggering spell %u from aura %u proc", triggerSpellId, GetId());
6560 target->CastSpell(target, triggerSpellId, true, NULL, this, GetCasterGUID());
6561}

6564void AuraEffect::HandleRaidProcFromChargeWithValueAuraProc(AuraApplication* aurApp, ProcEventInfo& /*eventInfo*/)
6565{
6566 Unit* target = aurApp->GetTarget();
6567
6568 // Currently only Prayer of Mending
6569 if (!(GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyName == SPELLFAMILY_PRIEST && GetSpellInfo()->SpellFamilyFlags[1] & 0x20))
6570 {
6571 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleRaidProcFromChargeWithValueAuraProc: received not handled spell: %u", GetId());
6572 return;
6573 }
6574 uint32 triggerSpellId = 33110;
6575
6576 int32 value = GetAmount();
6577
6578 int32 jumps = GetBase()->GetCharges();
6579
6580 // current aura expire on proc finish
6581 GetBase()->SetCharges(0);
6582 GetBase()->SetUsingCharges(true);
6583
6584 // next target selection
6585 if (jumps > 0)
6586 {
6587 if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
6588 {
6589 float radius = GetSpellEffectInfo()->CalcRadius(caster);
6590
6591 if (Unit* triggerTarget = target->GetNextRandomRaidMemberOrPet(radius))
6592 {
6593 target->CastCustomSpell(triggerTarget, GetId(), &value, NULL, NULL, true, NULL, this, GetCasterGUID());
6594 if (Aura* aura = triggerTarget->GetAura(GetId(), GetCasterGUID()))
6595 aura->SetCharges(jumps);
6596 }
6597 }
6598 }
6599
6600 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleRaidProcFromChargeWithValueAuraProc: Triggering spell %u from aura %u proc", triggerSpellId, GetId());
6601 target->CastCustomSpell(target, triggerSpellId, &value, NULL, NULL, true, NULL, this, GetCasterGUID());
6602}
6603
6604void AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellOnPowerAmountAuraProc(AuraApplication* aurApp, ProcEventInfo& eventInfo)
6605{
6606 // Power amount required to proc the spell
6607 int32 powerAmountRequired = GetAmount();
6608 // Power type required to proc
6609 Powers powerRequired = Powers(_effectInfo->MiscValue);
6610
6611 if (!powerRequired || !powerAmountRequired)
6612 {
6613 TC_LOG_ERROR("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellOnPowerAmountAuraProc: Spell %u have 0 PowerAmountRequired in EffectAmount[%d] or 0 PowerRequired in EffectMiscValue", GetId(), GetEffIndex());
6614 return /*false*/;
6615 }
6616
6617 Unit* triggerCaster = aurApp->GetTarget();
6618 Unit* triggerTarget = eventInfo.GetProcTarget();
6619
6620 if (triggerCaster->GetPower(powerRequired) != powerAmountRequired)
6621 return /*false*/;
6622
6623 uint32 triggerSpellId = _effectInfo->TriggerSpell;
6624 if (SpellInfo const* triggeredSpellInfo = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(triggerSpellId))
6625 {
6626 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellOnPowerAmountAuraProc: Triggering spell %u from aura %u proc", triggeredSpellInfo->Id, GetId());
6627 triggerCaster->CastSpell(triggerTarget, triggeredSpellInfo, true, nullptr, this);
6628 }
6629 else
6630 TC_LOG_DEBUG("spells", "AuraEffect::HandleProcTriggerSpellOnPowerAmountAuraProc: Could not trigger spell %u from aura %u proc, because the spell does not have an entry in Spell.dbc.", triggerSpellId, GetId());
6631}
6632
6633void AuraEffect::HandleAuraForceWeather(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
6634{
6635 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
6636 return;
6637
6638 Player* target = aurApp->GetTarget()->ToPlayer();
6639
6640 if (!target)
6641 return;
6642
6643 if (apply)
6644 {
6645 WorldPackets::Misc::Weather weather(WeatherState(GetMiscValue()), 1.0f);
6646 target->GetSession()->SendPacket(weather.Write());
6647 }
6648 else
6649 {
6650 // send weather for current zone
6651 if (Weather* weather = WeatherMgr::FindWeather(target->GetZoneId()))
6652 weather->SendWeatherUpdateToPlayer(target);
6653 else
6654 {
6655 if (!WeatherMgr::AddWeather(target->GetZoneId()))
6656 {
6657 // send fine weather packet to remove old weather
6658 WeatherMgr::SendFineWeatherUpdateToPlayer(target);
6659 }
6660 }
6661 }
6662}
6663
6664void AuraEffect::HandleEnableAltPower(AuraApplication const* aurApp, uint8 mode, bool apply) const
6665{
6666 if (!(mode & AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL))
6667 return;
6668
6669 uint32 altPowerId = GetMiscValue();
6670 UnitPowerBarEntry const* powerEntry = sUnitPowerBarStore.LookupEntry(altPowerId);
6671 if (!powerEntry)
6672 return;
6673
6674 if (apply)
6675 aurApp->GetTarget()->SetMaxPower(POWER_ALTERNATE_POWER, powerEntry->MaxPower);
6676 else
6677 aurApp->GetTarget()->SetMaxPower(POWER_ALTERNATE_POWER, 0);
6678}

6681{

6684
6685 if (Player* player = aurApp->GetTarget()->ToPlayer())
6686 player->SendSpellCategoryCooldowns();
6687}
